"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Iran has rejected Donald Trump's demand for a new deal to reopen the Strait of Hormuz. The closure of this important waterway has caused oil prices to rise. The situation could get worse if Iran captures the weapons officer from the downed F15 Eagle plane.\",            \"english_title\": \"Iran Rejects Trump's Demand\",            \"translated_version\": \"Ir\u00e1n ha dicho no a lo que Donald Trump quiere para abrir el Estrecho de Ormuz. Cerrar este lugar importante ha hecho que el precio del petr\u00f3leo suba. La situaci\u00f3n puede empeorar si Ir\u00e1n captura al oficial de armas del avi\u00f3n F15 Eagle ca\u00eddo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ir\u00e1n dice no a Trump\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Roberto Mazzarella has been hiding for over a year, using a fake name, according to the police.\",            \"english_title\": \"Roberto Mazzarella in Hiding\",            \"translated_version\": \"Roberto Mazzarella ha estado escondido por m\u00e1s de un a\u00f1o, usando un nombre falso, seg\u00fan la polic\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Roberto Mazzarella escondido\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The niece and grand-niece of Qasem Soleimani are being held by US Immigration and Customs Enforcement, officials have reported.\",            \"english_title\": \"Soleimani's Relatives Detained\",            \"translated_version\": \"La sobrina y la bisnieta de Qasem Soleimani est\u00e1n detenidas por la inmigraci\u00f3n de Estados Unidos, dicen los oficiales.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Familiares de Soleimani detenidos\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A Russian drone attack hit a busy area in a southern Ukrainian town on Saturday morning, injuring 21 people.\",            \"english_title\": \"Russian Drone Attack in Ukraine\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ataque de dron ruso golpe\u00f3 un \u00e1rea ocupada en un pueblo del sur de Ucrania el s\u00e1bado por la ma\u00f1ana, hiriendo a 21 personas.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque de dron ruso en Ucrania\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Cameroon's President Paul Biya, who is 93 years old, won his eighth term last year in an election that many disputed.\",            \"english_title\": \"Paul Biya Wins Eighth Term\",            \"translated_version\": \"El presidente de Camer\u00fan, Paul Biya, que tiene 93 a\u00f1os, gan\u00f3 su octavo mandato el a\u00f1o pasado en una elecci\u00f3n que muchos discutieron.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Paul Biya gana octavo mandato\"        }    ]}"